{"tid":1237054,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中大歷史系助教劉文斌唔洗做，錢照袋","createTime":"2019-06-17T13:55:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T09:16:40.000Z","uid":92339,"like":281,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"0e4e44ba29c8f27990807b88b84ac125eeb07ccf","tid":1237054,"uid":92339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:55:06.000Z","msg":"有關中大歷史系研究生兼助教劉文斌一事，中大歷史系於其網站發表聲明提到歷史系對事件「深表關注」，並「嚴肅處理當中」，部門更表示「暫時不安排該名同學在來年擔任助教工作」<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但係！！！</span></strong><br />\nUGC funded 大學既研究生每個月受政府資助，因此一般會為學部做助教<br />\n佢仍家只係唔洗做 TA<br />\n但完全冇提及有處分或終止學位<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">換句話講：佢係以後每個月唔洗做，繼續攞我地納稅人錢！！！</span></strong></span><br />\n我地根本冇贏過！！！！<br />\n<br />\n中大依家根本係求求其其咁扮處理左就 Close file！！<br />\n我地唔可以俾佢得過且過！<br />\n<br />\n既然研究生收得納稅人錢，就受得公眾監察<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我哋個個都係持份者！！</span></strong><br />\n如果各位巴絲係中大畢業生，就更加受影響！<br />\n今次事件直頭係影響中大學術 Integrity, 有損校譽！！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">建議大家繼續打去中大研究院或電郵研究院 &amp; Dean &amp; department head<br />\n逼佢地表態同處分劉文斌，最好褫奪每月 studentship 或學位！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n等條大陸仔個個月唔洗做 Un un 腳攞 17k 咁爽皮！"},{"pid":"0de7a1c6d399583696eba535a99a0f3a17fd5870","tid":1237054,"uid":92339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:55:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cec5ba56729a057cb86839eba73bd59afc2de3b1","tid":1237054,"uid":92339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:57:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df6b70a0c856a1666e2eda723b1bdcdae270628b","tid":1237054,"uid":92339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:59:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a5a3d08a17fce0803293c544d32bc87a4b04cb84","tid":1237054,"uid":92339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T14:00:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f32d6bcd76b8fd5134b9d7b00e8efc6320e63ffd","tid":1237054,"uid":48222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T14:06:09.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"918ee55a8cd9378d2df0a4a690621bbe541a97f0","tid":1237054,"uid":92339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T14:18:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"362c4fce43b7fa3b8013581dce3847620e0e31ff","tid":1237054,"uid":92339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T14:32:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c8dd985277660d5c885e484300c13c72d9874b3","tid":1237054,"uid":92339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T14:35:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"080397cdfde7b4f4816b2de5befe40e5652266ed","tid":1237054,"uid":249794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T14:57:59.000Z","msg":"推~"},{"pid":"caa0496f90d556ce6bfc67811880f732f7015e45","tid":1237054,"uid":55775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T14:59:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d4816f3cd9a46cc71901d5dcae1f1e7aca6c6247","tid":1237054,"uid":111418,"like":81,"dislike":0,"score":81,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T14:59:52.000Z","msg":"劉文斌  廈門大學歷史文學士   中大歷史mphil year1<br />\n題目：明代經濟     指導教授：卜永堅(卜生好野)<br />\n2018-2019學年sem 1擔任tutor課程：無<br />\n2018-2019學年sem 2擔任tutor課程：HIST5574(Ma course) 講師：鄧聰 (佢只係掛名Ta，實質做助教野都係蕭生蕭錦華，佢都係行行企企)<br />\n<br />\n好啦你可能會問點解條仆街會無Ta workload咁濟，因為條友話自己唔識廣東話同英文差，但係好多courses都用廣東話教，所以department第一個sem就唔洗佢做Ta，到第二個sem又求其加佢落個ma course度，乜都無做過仲好意思話肥學生，收皮啦。所以條垃圾大陸仔根本係貴族咁成年喺度9 fing，然後每個月白拎助學金，根本對其他研究生就好唔公平，今次仲要兇 local啲UG學生，真係火都黎，今次至少一定要學系扣佢studentship!"},{"pid":"7f43631792ad180dbea49bc131f9eb5d774b6f1b","tid":1237054,"uid":92339,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"d4816f3cd9a46cc71901d5dcae1f1e7aca6c6247","tid":1237054,"uid":111418,"like":81,"dislike":0,"score":81,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T14:59:52.000Z","msg":"劉文斌  廈門大學歷史文學士   中大歷史mphil year1<br />\n題目：明代經濟     指導教授：卜永堅(卜生好野)<br />\n2018-2019學年sem 1擔任tutor課程：無<br />\n2018-2019學年sem 2擔任tutor課程：HIST5574